item.title: CVE-2015-10048|2024-08-06T08:58:26.620Z -- bmattoso -- desafio_buzz_woody
item.description: A vulnerability was found in bmattoso desafio_buzz_woody. It has been rated as critical. This issue affects some unknown processing. The manipulation leads to sql injection. The identifier of the patch is cb8220cbae06082c969b1776fcb2fdafb3a1006b. It is recommended to apply a patch to fix this issue. The identifier VDB-218357 was assigned to this vulnerability.
